HEADWORD: Myriologue
<hw>Myr"i*o*logue</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>myriologue</ets>, <ets>myriologie</ets>, NGr. <?/, <?/, fr. Gr.
